🗣 Mesut Ozil when asked if he is heading for an Arsenal exit: &ldquo;No. I have a contract until the summer of 2021 and I will be staying until then.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;You can go through difficult times, like this, but that is no reason to run away and I&rsquo;m not going to. I&rsquo;m here until at least 2021.&quot;
